name: Gigantosaurus
overview: Four curious young dinosaur friends explore the mystery of Gigantosaurus, the largest, fiercest dinosaur of all, facing their individual fears and working together to solve problems during their many adventures.

episodes.name: Mazu Takes A Chance
episodes.overview: Mazu must do the impossible to protect a helpless dragonfly from raptors!

episodes.name: The Lost Egg
episodes.overview: Rocky suppresses his “tough dino” side and learns to be gentle with an egg he’s found.

episodes.name: Saving Ayati
episodes.overview: When Ayati loses her balance and falls over, Mazu must come up with a big idea to help.

episodes.name: The Crevice
episodes.overview: A large crevice rips through the ground and traps the four little dinos in Giganto's path.

episodes.name: The Island
episodes.overview: Timid Bill and brave Rocky end up stranded on an island, however Rocky suddenly becomes the scared one!

episodes.name: Don't Cave In
episodes.overview: Trey warns the little dinos about a cave monster named “Shriekasaurus”.

episodes.name: Because Triceratops!
episodes.overview: Tiny performs a triceratops rite of passage!

episodes.name: Rock Out
episodes.overview: Rocky sets out to prove that he's the ultimate tough guy, like Giganto, but discovers that everyone needs help sometimes.

episodes.name: Air Archie
episodes.overview: Mazu makes Archie a pair of wings to help him fly.

episodes.name: The Imitator
episodes.overview: Marsh copies Rocky's every move while Rocky copies Giganto.

episodes.name: The Biggest Hero
episodes.overview: Rocky gets jealous when Tiny suddenly becomes the go-to hero!

episodes.name: Think Quick
episodes.overview: Mazu may be a slow runner but is a quick thinker.

episodes.name: Please Don't Pick the Flowers
episodes.overview: Bill accidentally changes Cretacia’s ecosystem when he eats too many rare swamp flowers.

episodes.name: No Joke
episodes.overview: Dilo pulls pranks on the dinos!

episodes.name: Seeing Stars
episodes.overview: Mazu and her three besties map the stars.

episodes.name: A Tiny Triumph
episodes.overview: Tiny’s artistic skills are put to use when the dinos are lost in the desert.

episodes.name: Giganto's Laugh
episodes.overview: Tiny and Mazu treat Giganto's toothache.

episodes.name: Treasure!
episodes.overview: Every dino in Cretacia tries to claim a beautiful pebble!

episodes.name: Invisi-Bill
episodes.overview: Bill's friends pretend he is invisible so he can win at hide-and-seek.

episodes.name: Patchy Sees the Light
episodes.overview: Mazu invents eyeglasses to help nearsighted Patchy.

episodes.name: Differing Dino Tales
episodes.overview: When a runaway boulder ruins Mazu's invention, she sets out to find what set it in motion.

episodes.name: Big Bill
episodes.overview: Bill is tired of being a little brachiosaurus, so he looks for the secret to growing big.

episodes.name: Talent-O-Saurus
episodes.overview: Rocky decides not to practice for a talent show but his partner in the show is Giganto.

episodes.name: Marsh the Raptor
episodes.overview: Marsh is tricked by raptors to play a game, but they're really trying to sabotage Giganto.

episodes.name: The Best Crest
episodes.overview: Rocky has to get nectar from a special flower to get his Giganto cards back from the raptors.

episodes.name: The Drought
episodes.overview: Tiny and Bill accidentally clog up Cretacia's water source while playing in the cave.

episodes.name: Racing Giganto
episodes.overview: Mazu invents the world's first go-carts to beat Giganto in a race.

episodes.name: Bill's Night Feast
episodes.overview: When Bill's food stash is raided, he makes it his mission to find the culprit.

episodes.name: The Big Mean Green
episodes.overview: When everyone blames Giganto for damaging the lake, the Dinos try to prove his innocence.

episodes.name: How Giganto Got His Roar
episodes.overview: Rocky wants to roar like Giganto, so he sets out to capture the beast's roar in a coconut.

episodes.name: The Challenge
episodes.overview: Turf rights to the playground are at stake when the raptors challenge the four Dinos to a game of basketball.

episodes.name: Giganto's Boss
episodes.overview: Rocky tries to convince everyone that he's the Giganto-Whisperer.

episodes.name: Follow the Leader
episodes.overview: Rocky gets carried away being the leader in a game.

episodes.name: An Artist is Born
episodes.overview: Tiny helps Trey find his inner artist when Trey injures himself in a tree toppling accident.

episodes.name: Bill's Broken Promise
episodes.overview: Bill is tasked with inviting Giganto to Rocky's birthday party.

episodes.name: Born Tree
episodes.overview: Tiny grows attached to a sapling tree and isn't ready to let go when the tree is ready to be planted.

episodes.name: A Giganto Power
episodes.overview: Rocky wants a tail as powerful as Giganto's, but with great power comes great responsibility!

episodes.name: Crying Wolfasaurus
episodes.overview: Bill discovers that 'crying wolf' lets him avoid doing things he doesn't want to do.

episodes.name: The Five Friends
episodes.overview: The dinos have a falling out.

episodes.name: A Tiny Favor
episodes.overview: Tiny, the little dino must repay the favor and honor Triceratops Code.

episodes.name: Coco Bill
episodes.overview: When Rugo tries to collect all of the coconuts in Cretacia, Bill sets out to get them back!

episodes.name: Brothers and Sisters
episodes.overview: Tiny and Totor discover they have a lot in common.

episodes.name: The Floating Stone
episodes.overview: After they interrupt her meditation, Terminonator keeps Tiny and Bill hostage until Rocky and Mazu bring her a mythical floating stone.

episodes.name: The Light in the Storm
episodes.overview: Bill and Marsh get separated from the others in the fog, and a storm is on the way. To make matters worse, Bill lacks confidence in himself as a leader

episodes.name: Frozen Giganto
episodes.overview: When Giganto makes a long absence, the ecosystem order spirals out of control, sending the friends on a hunt for the large dino in the frozen lands. He turns out to be frozen by an avalanche, and their mission? Melt the ice around him.

episodes.name: Dinosia
episodes.overview: Ayati directs the friends to Dinosia for new things to discover, only to find that it was only a fib to lead them on a new adventure in Cretacia.

episodes.name: The Shortest Day
episodes.overview: Tiny sets out to plan a party on the shortest day of the year.

episodes.name: Mazu's Comet
episodes.overview: Mazu is determined to see her comet, but when things take a rough turn, she gets help from those she had helped before.

episodes.name: A Very Sticky Problem
episodes.overview: An incident with coconuts and tar leaves Mazu and Cror stuck back-to-back. The two end up sharing an unusual bonding experience as they try to get unstuck.

episodes.name: Forward Marsh
episodes.overview: Rocky rushes the crew to get the best spots to watch the winter lights, but his impatience gets the better of him and his shortcuts lead to disaster. Luckily, taking it slow got them a good spot.

episodes.name: Goodbye, Giganto! Part 1
episodes.overview: Mount Oblivion gets clogged with a meteorite and, fearing a lava eruption, the herd is forced to move, with Giganto left behind. They friends decide to prevent this by breaking the meteor.

episodes.name: Goodbye, Giganto! Part 2
episodes.overview: Giganto leaves for parts unknown. The Terminonator then takes over Cretacia, leading the friends to rebel.

episodes.name: Termy, Come, Home!
episodes.overview: Termy leaves Cretecia which the locals briefly enjoy, but they soon want her back when her absence causes problems in the pond.

episodes.name: Rocky the Record Breaker
episodes.overview: When the young dinosaurs finds a tablet about someone who holds many records, Rocky tries to break any of them.

episodes.name: Once in a Pink Moon
episodes.overview: Bill is less interested in change, and is declining any invitation from his friends who want to show him something new.

episodes.name: A Giganto Gallery
episodes.overview: Tiny gets jealous when Marsh's art starts getting more attention despite not being as good as hers.

episodes.name: Giganto Games
episodes.overview: In a multi-sporting event featuring teams of two dinosaurs, Cror encourages Bill to employ illegal tactics to gain some advantage.

episodes.name: Coconuts for Coco-phones
episodes.overview: Mazu creates mobile phones out of coconuts, and gives one to every dinosaur in Cretacia.

episodes.name: Mini Giganto
episodes.overview: Rocky has a statuette of Giganto which he no longer plays, and his friends suggest he should give it to someone, but Rocky finds it hard.

episodes.name: Singosaurus
episodes.overview: Cror and Trey need to get over their differences as they are selected to sing together at the show.

episodes.name: A New Home for Leon
episodes.overview: Rocky, Bill, Tiny, and Mazu befriend a sea turtle named Leon, and try to find him a home in their neighborhood.

episodes.name: Mirror Mirror
episodes.overview: Tiny becomes addicted looking at her face on a reflective rock.

episodes.name: I Heart Giganto
episodes.overview: Tiny ponders on how to spend Togetherness Day with Giganto.

episodes.name: Guardians of the Herds
episodes.overview: Hegan and Trey teach Rocky, Bill, Tiny, and Mazu about keeping Cretacia safe for its inhabitants, but an impatient Rocky unwittingly makes things worse.

episodes.name: Ayati's Big Birthday
episodes.overview: The four little dinos want to give Ayati presents for her 200th birthday.

episodes.name: A New Best T
episodes.overview: The Raptors bring T-Rex to Cretacia and Rocky finds him good fun to play with.

episodes.name: Top Dino
episodes.overview: Tiny becomes the Top Dino for the day.

episodes.name: Dinos to the Moon
episodes.overview: Mazu creates a rocket to fly to the moon. Unfortunately, her failed attempt to fly to the moon lands herself, her friends, and Rugo in an unknown part of Cretacia.

episodes.name: Don't Bug Bill
episodes.overview: Bill runs off with Marsh when Mazu showcases the bugs. T decides to follow them and scare Bill by pretending to be a bug.

episodes.name: Super Marsh
episodes.overview: Marsh admires the four little dinos and their incredible talents that are like super powers.

episodes.name: Secret-Saurus
episodes.overview: When Rocky is unhappy with his present from Tiny, he gets rid of it.

episodes.name: Party of One
episodes.overview: Bill tries to have a party to celebrate getting the first coconuts of Spring, but his friends decide to take it over.

episodes.name: Dino Dash
episodes.overview: The four young dinos create a new board game. While going out to build the volcano, Tiny and Mazu disagree on whether it should be artistic or scientific.

episodes.name: Good Idea
episodes.overview: The snow is melting. Mazu and Trey have different ideas on how to prevent Cretacia from being flooded.

episodes.name: Archaeop-Tricks
episodes.overview: When T-Rex teases Archie about being unable to fly, Mazu comes to his defense.

episodes.name: Blind to Fashion
episodes.overview: Giganto starts a trend when a banana peel gets stuck to the top of his head.

episodes.name: Plink, Plonk, and Plunk
episodes.overview: The four dinos meet three new friends named Plink, Plonk and Plunk.

episodes.name: The Caterpillar Contest
episodes.overview: The dinos have a contest to see who can take care of their caterpillar the best.

episodes.name: The Star Stone
episodes.overview: Mazu wants to be the first to find a meteorite that landed in the desert.

episodes.name: Capa-Bill
episodes.overview: Leon likes to help Bill, but realizes he has to learn to do things for himself.

episodes.name: Rugo the Roommate
episodes.overview: When Rugo's burrow floods, the four dinos invite her to live with them temporarily.

episodes.name: The Winner
episodes.overview: Tiny has hidden colored, egg-shaped stones around Cretacia for a treasure hunt.

episodes.name: The Big Ig
episodes.overview: Iggy is the proud caretaker of a berry bog but must challenge T to a game of Capture the Flag to remain in charge.

episodes.name: Saving Snugglesaurus
episodes.overview: Rocky has to watch his baby cousin for the day.

episodes.name: The Singing Chef
episodes.overview: Tiny writes a musical called "Mighty Dinosaurs" but she can't find the right dino to play the lead, until she finds out that Bill can sing very well when he is preparing food.

episodes.name: The Dino Drone
episodes.overview: Hegan is jealous of Mazu's drone that can fly anywhere in Cretacia.

episodes.name: Scary Bill
episodes.overview: Bill ventures out into the scary darkness to find ingredients for his pumpkin bread.

episodes.name: The Dino Finder
episodes.overview: After helping Mazu win hide-and-seek, Rocky names himself the greatest dino finder ever.

episodes.name: The Snow Cave
episodes.overview: Bill, Mazu and Rocky head to the Frozen Land in search of a snow cave just as a blizzard comes.

episodes.name: Good Dino
episodes.overview: Tiny wants to create a statue of Cretacia's greatest hero out of a big boulder.

episodes.name: The Time Capsule
episodes.overview: When Rugo accidentally unearths a time capsule Ayati made with her friend 100 years ago, the four little dinos decide they want to make one too.

episodes.name: Marsh O Saurus
episodes.overview: Marsh wants to be like Giganto.

episodes.name: The Great Sled Chase
episodes.overview: A great chase ensues when T takes the sled filled with gifts for himself.

episodes.name: Dino-Sitting
episodes.overview: Rocky, Mazu Tiny and Bill find themselves with little siblings, and Mazu thinks she can watch them all.

episodes.name: Master of the Elements
episodes.overview: When Rocky learns that no one has made it to the end of the maze, he's determined to be the first!

episodes.name: Cretacia's School for Dinos
episodes.overview: The four little dinos open a school to share their knowledge with all Cretacians, but Cror decides to send Totor in to ruin the school.

episodes.name: A Brush with Sadness
episodes.overview: Tiny mourns the loss of her favourite paintbrush when it falls apart.

episodes.name: What If?
episodes.overview: The dinos imagine what the world would be like if they were allowed to do whatever they wanted.

episodes.name: Bill's Nose Knows
episodes.overview: Bill is known for having the best sniffer in town.

episodes.name: Big Brother, Big Sister
episodes.overview: When Tiny's little sister comes along, Trey spends a great deal of time playing with her -- and not much time with Tiny.

episodes.name: A Giant Success
episodes.overview: When Giganto assists the kids, Tiny wants to thank him by throwing a tea party.

episodes.name: The Stick in the Stone
episodes.overview: Trey and T both think they're the toughest.

episodes.name: A New Big Guy
episodes.overview: When a big, new dinosaur arrives in Cretacia, Bill's instincts are telling him to stay away.

episodes.name: Battle of the Titans
episodes.overview: Spino, the massive villain, is intent on terrorizing.

episodes.name: Ayati's Great Adventure
episodes.overview: The baby dinos are proving to be a handful, especially when Ayati tries to care for them.

episodes.name: King of the Horseshoe Crabs
episodes.overview: The horseshoe crabs treat Rocky like a king after he inadvertently does them a favour.

episodes.name: Bubble Bill
episodes.overview: When Bill realizes just how indestructible weird fish bubbles are, he decides to live inside one.

episodes.name: The Perfect Bone
episodes.overview: Rugo and Ignatius each find the same, perfect, semicircle-shaped bone.

episodes.name: Adventures in Egg Sitting
episodes.overview: The four little dinos are tasked with watching Hegan's eggs, which are soon to hatch.

episodes.name: Rainbow's End
episodes.overview: When the dinos learn about a treasure at the end of a rainbow, Rocky is determined to find it!

episodes.name: Termy Steps Out
episodes.overview: Termy wants to visit her good friend Hegan's new babies, Pride and Joy.

episodes.name: The Tooth Fairy
episodes.overview: Rocky is excited when Giganto loses a tooth because that means the tooth fairy will visit and leave loot. The Raptors decide to have him lead them to Giganto's lair so they can take his bone.

episodes.name: Wait For It!
episodes.overview: Tiny, Rocky and Bill have a hard time being patient waiting for the lulu fruit to change color.

episodes.name: Mr. Careful
episodes.overview: Mazu borrows Rocky's kart and flies it as a plane, but he doesn't know how to fly.

episodes.name: Tiny Tells
episodes.overview: Tiny likes the attention she gets from announcing the news so she starts a news service. Unfortunately, she soon starts getting carried away with her tall tales, and Spino soon shows up to cause more trouble.

episodes.name: Sleeping Spino
episodes.overview: The dinos have to find another place to sleep for the night, but Mazu can't sleep.

episodes.name: Friendship Cards
episodes.overview: Tiny wants to help the dinos get along, so she invents a game to pair one dino with another. Mazu is partnered with Totor, Rocky with Cror, Bill with T-Rex and Tiny with Patchy.

episodes.name: The Missing Manual
episodes.overview: Mount Oblivion seems like it's going to blow, and Mazu needs to find her book to stop it.

episodes.name: Brother Bill
episodes.overview: Bill starts to feel like his sister might like Rocky more than him.

episodes.name: Tricksteratops
episodes.overview: Missy is good at magic tricks, so they encourage her to do a magic show.

episodes.name: Council of Wise Dinos
episodes.overview: When a spot opens on the council, Mazu applies.

episodes.name: Rockatastrophe
episodes.overview: Rocky becomes so fixated on helping that he doesn't stop and think about what he is doing.

episodes.name: The Bravest
episodes.overview: Bill realizes bravery is doing something you're afraid of to help someone else.

episodes.name: The Sleepover
episodes.overview: After Mazu's science experiments backfires, the dinos have to evacuate the den for the night.

episodes.name: Master of Nothing
episodes.overview: Bill teaches Missy how to bake a pie, but Missy's pie turns out better than Bill's.

episodes.name: Hooray for Totor
episodes.overview: When Totor sees other dinos get awarded for their talents, he sets out to find his talent.

episodes.name: Sleepless in Cretacia
episodes.overview: The little dinos go sledding and Marsh wants to join them, but he hasn't had his nap yet.

episodes.name: The Walnut Goblin
episodes.overview: On the way to visit Hegan, Bill and Tiny find a walnut field and they search for nuts.

episodes.name: Marsh's Lullaby
episodes.overview: The dinos discover Marsh can sing lullabies that put dinos to sleep.

episodes.name: Fantastic Stories
episodes.overview: When Rocky sees all the attention the babies give to Giganto, he gets a bit jealous.

episodes.name: Giganto's Nightlight
episodes.overview: While out for a stroll one evening, Mazu's brother wants to know about a glowing rock that they encounter.

episodes.name: A Job Half Done
episodes.overview: Rocky has to clean up his act in order to save his friends from danger.

episodes.name: The Bill Way
episodes.overview: Bill harvests cycad leaves the Bill Way.

episodes.name: Bye-Bye Butterfly
episodes.overview: The dinos are excited to see the Empress butterflies as they pass by but when Rocky throws them off course they are in trouble.

episodes.name: Mystery Hunters
episodes.overview: When word of a monster reaches the dinos, Mazu is determined to find it.

episodes.name: Watching You
episodes.overview: When the raptors swipe pies from the dinos, they get more than they expected when they swipe Leena too.

episodes.name: Raiders of the Lost Shell
episodes.overview: Rocky plays with Tiny's cymbal shell without asking and breaks it.

episodes.name: Super Dilo
episodes.overview: The four dinos think Dilo is quite the hero when he protects them from Spinosaurus.

episodes.name: Silly Saurus
episodes.overview: Trey assigns Tiny the task of creating a triceratops training course for their baby sister Tory.

episodes.name: Rock A Bye Baby
episodes.overview: Marsh wishes he had a little brother or sister, so he makes some out of rocks.

episodes.name: The Juggle Buddies
episodes.overview: Bill enlists Totor to do juggling act with him to win a trophy at the show.

episodes.name: Don't Look Back
episodes.overview: Rocky is excited to run in the race, but when Rolo decides to run the race too, Rocky gets annoyed.

episodes.name: Mama Termy
episodes.overview: Termy is coerced into babysitting Pride and Joy.

episodes.name: The Shadow Show
episodes.overview: Mazu invents a projector where she can show the shadows of puppets up on the wall.
